ed and cherished by the ancients. But its distinctive peppery taste is really a modern invention</p><p class="sc-c0f26063-0 sc-c0f26063-8 Yva-Dw jfoikg">Massimo Mazzotti</p></div><div class="sc-c0f26063-4 gLchsi"></div></div></a><a href="/essays/tech-vexed-how-digital-life-threatens-our-capacity-for-awe"><div class="sc-c0f26063-7 gTsRyU"><div type="essay" class="sc-31fe189a-2 hDRjbu"><img alt="A man floating in the sea beneath a dramatic, stormy sky with large, dark clouds." loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 960px) 45vw, (max-width: 1440px) 30vw, 430px" srcSet="https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/a662a4aa-bc17-426a-82bd-89e58e2f7103/essay-heat_storm.jpg?width=256&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 256w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/a662a4aa-bc17-426a-82bd-89e58e2f7103/essay-heat_storm.jpg?width=384&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 384w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/a662a4aa-bc17-426a-82bd-89e58e2f7103/essay-heat_storm.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 640w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/a662a4aa-bc17-426a-82bd-89e58e2f7103/essay-heat_storm.jpg?width=750&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 750w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/a662a4aa-bc17-426a-82bd-89e58e2f7103/essay-heat_storm.jpg?width=828&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 828w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/a662a4aa-bc17-426a-82bd-89e58e2f7103/essay-heat_storm.jpg?width=1080&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1080w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/a662a4aa-bc17-426a-82bd-89e58e2f7103/essay-heat_storm.jpg?width=1200&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1200w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/a662a4aa-bc17-426a-82bd-89e58e2f7103/essay-heat_storm.jpg?width=1920&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1920w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/a662a4aa-bc17-426a-82bd-89e58e2f7103/essay-heat_storm.jpg?width=2048&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 2048w, https:/